page.title: 10MY JAM-PACKED DAY
page.content: I woke up at 6.52am, when my alarm went off. I was still half asleep. My mum shouted at me to come downstairs. It took me ages to get out of bed. I went downstairs. It was 7.25am. I had Shreddies and marmalade sandwiches with a cup of tea. After breakfast I went upstairs and wasted time. Then I cleaned my teeth with Colgate and Crest, mixed. I washed my face and went to the loo. It was 7.45am.I got my swimming kit ready and put talc inside my hat then I stuffed it all in a plastic bag. Then I got my homework ready. By that time it was 8.00am, my mum shouted at me to come and get my piano practice done. My dad had already gone to work. I did my practice with great difficulty as Melissa my sister was playing her recorder as well. When I finished it was 8.30am
